# Databases Laboratory Work Nr 1

# Title

Installation and Configuration of SQL Server 2017

# Prerequisites

Microsot Sql Server Management Studio 2017

“Microsoft SQL Server 2017 pas cu pas” course book

# Objectives

Installation and Configuration of SQL Server 2017

Establishing connection to servers	

Creation of Logins in SQL Server

# Tasks

Learn to perform

Server Registration

Server Exclusion	

Server registration modification	

Windows Authentication	

Mixed Authentication

Creation of Logins

