# Conclusion

The installation and configuration of the SQL Server Manager 2017 is a quick 
and easy process. It is an integrated environment for managing SQL infrastructures. 
It can be used to access, configure, manage, administer and develop all components of 
SQL Server, such as: databases, tables, diagrams, indexes, views, schemes, triggers, 
functions, rules, etc.
